schema.name: creator
schema.sql: CREATE TABLE "creator" (`id` integer PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT NOT NULL, `user_created` varchar(255) NULL, `date_created` datetime NULL, `user_updated` char(36) NULL, `date_updated` datetime NULL, `full_name` varchar(255) NULL, `number` varchar(255) NULL, `mail_id` varchar(255) NULL, `about_you` text NULL, `yt_subscribers` varchar(255) NULL, `yt_engagement` varchar(255) NULL, `yt_content_niche` varchar(255) NULL, `yt_deliverables` varchar(255) NULL, `yt_details_gender_ratio` varchar(255) NULL, `yt_details_age_to` varchar(255) NULL, `yt_details_top_cities` varchar(255) NULL, `ig_followers` varchar(255) NULL, `ig_engagement` varchar(255) NULL, `ig_content_niche` varchar(255) NULL, `ig_deliverables` varchar(255) NULL, `ig_details_gender_ratio` varchar(255) NULL, `ig_details_age_to` varchar(255) NULL, `ig_details_top_cities` varchar(255) NULL, `user` char(36) NULL, CONSTRAINT `creator_user_created_foreign` FOREIGN KEY (`user_created`) REFERENCES `directus_users` (`id`), CONSTRAINT `creator_user_updated_foreign` FOREIGN KEY (`user_updated`) REFERENCES `directus_users` (`id`), CONSTRAINT `creator_user_foreign` FOREIGN KEY (`user`) REFERENCES `directus_users` (`id`) ON DELETE SET NULL)
